PrecisRegulations Amending the PACIFIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS by increasing the port-to-port pilotage fee from $600 to $700 per assignment, and by introducing a surcharge for the purpose of creating a fund to cover the cost of replacing the pilot boats at certain locations, effective May 1, 1999.
